, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1354684,"age":7,"year":"1200","julianDay":2159351,"description":"The Christian territory controlled the Kingdoms of Aragon, Navarre, and Castile.","jurisdictionLevel":3}],"lifeSummary":"When Agnes de Torroja was born in 1193, in Cardona, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain, her father, Ramón de Torroja y Cervera, was 16 and her mother, Sybille de Santa Fe, was 23. She married Ramon VIII Folch de Cardona on 20 September 1208. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 2 daughters. She died in 1245, at the age of 52."},"et":{"1193–       1245":"1193–1245","1193–1245":"1193–1245","1190–1241":"1190–1241","1209–1293":"1209–1293","1220–Female":"1220–Surnud","1240–1276":"1240–1276","1177–1195":"1177–1195","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","1190":"1190","1220":"1220","1241":"1241","1240":"1240","1195":"1195","1293":"1293","1193":"1193","1170":"1170","23 August 1241":"23. august 1241","ABT 1187":"umbes 1187","20 September 1208":"20. september 1208","1245":"1245","       1245":"1245","1200":"1200","1177":"1177","1276":"1276","1209":"1209","Solsona, Catalogne, Espagne":"Bisbat de Solsona, Catalunya, Hispaania","Espagne":"Hispaania","Cardona, Cataluña, Espagne":"Cardona, Barcelona, Catalunya, Hispaania","Arbeca, Lleida, Catalonia, Spain":"Arbeca, Lleida, Catalunya, Hispaania","Cardona, Barcelona, Catalonia, Spain":"Cardona, Barcelona, Catalunya, Hispaania"},"fi":{"1193–       1245":"1193–1245","1193–1245":"1193–1245","1190–1241":"1190–1241","1209–1293":"1209–1293","1220–Female":"1220–Kuollut","1240–1276":"1240–1276","1177–1195":"1177–1195","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","1190":"1190","1220":"1220","1241":"1241","1240":"1240","1195":"1195","1293":"1293","1193":"1193","1170":"1170","23 August 1241":"23. elokuuta 1241","ABT 1187":"noin 1187","20 September 1208":"20. syyskuuta 1208","1245":"1245","       1245":"1245","1200":"1200","1177":"1177","127